msg":"梁右嘉<br />\n梁又嘉<br />\n梁佑嘉<br />\n梁祐嘉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T03:41:46.000Z","msg":"梁左嘉<br />\n梁佐嘉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"焗袏減"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"究竟我睇左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d0a5608434d1f5b79352d7759c97b3abcd3721","tid":1934104,"uid":2727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"who？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddd8f7dcb020dbd615a3cd19aa227443007d72b","tid":1934104,"uid":272819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"快 你愛到很快 快過秒針拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明勁難聽 但又停不下來聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17d1df15e7c2e0b618eb888c96c53cef68806ec","tid":1934104,"uid":10062,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"個名好難接受, 好困擾囉...糧油加....通脹咩....而家生活已經好困難 不如直接叫 Inflation Leung 啦!<br />\n<br />\n做農民既就鐘意 &ldquo;糧油加&rdquo; o者, 種得多賺得多嗎<br />\n<br />\n唔知呢個名邊個改啦&hellip;. 如果係屋企改, 阿爸可能真係務農 如果連老豆都唔認既就一定出人頭地. 聖保祿都係咁上下, 你睇人地幾出名丫, 仲有學校用佢命名添<br />\n<br />\n再唔係可以唱阿 Sam 個首 &ldquo;加價熱潮&rdquo; 糖又加！糧油加! 幾好聽呀, 一定掂<br />\n<br />\n其實金銀業貿易場應該邀請做吉祥物, 等D人見到就諗起通脹, 係咁買金抗通脹囉<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就去聯儲局, 日日對住伯南克, 橫掂佢咁想適度通脹, 咪滿足佢囉 不過唔好對太耐, 我驚佢受不了囉, I mean 惡性通脹呀, OK?<br />\n<br />\n唉!早日放工, 座地鐵(我呢D窮向左走向右走唔座地鐵, 唔通馬車咩), 見到有個燈箱廣告, 有一華人女子, 雙手托下巴, do 起個嘴. 心入面都無話 &ldquo;這麼&hellip;..&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不過望一望個名&hellip;係&hellip;係....真係呀! 不禁呀左一聲 &ldquo;通脹!! 放過我啦!!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n其實, 我已經好慘, 係呢個通脹既年代, 唔好市講話二手飯都可能要食, 為左用少D錢, 唔怕老實講, 底褲都要著完前面反轉再著多一日, 點解咁做呢? 因為可以洗少一次, 用少一次水, 真係想用少D錢, 對抗通脹!<br />\n<br />\n但竟然, 放左工都要見到呢張 poster ?! Inflation Leung, 放過我啦!!!"},{"pid":"21322bf0e3748df0d7b3af8492249f988c52b711","tid":1934104,"uid":71330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"佢同陳柏宇老婆點分？"},{"pid":"ad23276f381c79226537296e6ffa6975bba0b7d6","tid":1934104,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ddd8f7dcb020dbd615a3cd19aa227443007d72b","tid":1934104,"uid":272819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"快 你愛到很快 快過秒針拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明勁難聽 但又停不下來聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:08:08.000Z","msg":"仲記得嗰陣廣告係撚咁播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683f1e29a32eb7a5640f5d02860e0330ac1253f9","tid":1934104,"uid":227597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"到底佢做錯咗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd537c887dd28359f9dbde45a6395e3941c9b388","tid":1934104,"uid":350194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:20:57.000Z","msg":"佢嗰首快幾入耳 但點解冇點紅過"},{"pid":"0a6430cd4d8344de1fd28f8872d394eded2ad838","tid":1934104,"uid":249160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21322bf0e3748df0d7b3af8492249f988c52b711","tid":1934104,"uid":71330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"佢同陳柏宇老婆點分？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:22:12.000Z","msg":"唔講都唔覺<br />\n兩個都樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33eecda6e78f718b6281c38f4ce7b15b7e32949c","tid":1934104,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95538a850392368dac1702c4e5c277d10a3dbe5f","tid":1934104,"uid":54079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b89761fabbdf3522712633de00fb82ab349c9214","tid":1934104,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a14af76163788ba28859644f4d8b56fd98ac